text: == Events == *Egbert of Wessex defeats Beornwulf of Mercia at Ellandun. Kent, Surrey, Sussex and Essex submit to Wessex and East Anglia acknowledges Egbert as overlord. *Emperor Louis the Pious of the Franks wars against the Wends and Sorbs. == Births == *Louis II, Holy Roman Emperor (d. 875) == Deaths ==
